      "description": "\n<div>Under Mirabeau Bridge the river slips away <br>\n<\/div>\n<div>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 And lovers <br>\n<\/div>\n<div>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Must I be reminded <br>\n<\/div>\n<div>Joy came always after pain <br>\n<\/div>\n<div><br><\/div>\n<div><br><\/div>\n<div>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0The night is a clock chiming <br>\n<\/div>\n<div>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0The days go by not I <br>\n<\/div>\n<div><br><\/div>\n<div><br><\/div>\n<div>We're face to face and hand in hand <br>\n<\/div>\n<div>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0While under the bridges <br>\n<\/div>\n<div>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Of embrace expire <br>\n<\/div>\n<div>Eternal tired tidal eyes <br>\n<\/div>\n<div><br><\/div>\n<div><br><\/div>\n<div>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0The night is a clock chiming <br>\n<\/div>\n<div>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0The days go by not I <br>\n<\/div>\n<div><br><\/div>\n<div><br><\/div>\n<div>Love elapses like the river <br>\n<\/div>\n<div>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0Love goes by <br>\n<\/div>\n<div>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Poor life is indolent <br>\n<\/div>\n<div>And expectation always violent <br>\n<\/div>\n<div><br><\/div>\n<div><br><\/div>\n<div>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0The night is a clock chiming <br>\n<\/div>\n<div>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0The days go by not I <br>\n<\/div>\n<div><br><\/div>\n<div><br><\/div>\n<div>The days and equally the weeks elapse <br>\n<\/div>\n<div>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0The past remains the past <br>\n<\/div>\n<div>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Love remains lost <br>\n<\/div>\n<div>Under Mirabeau Bridge the river slips away <br>\n<\/div>\n<div><br><\/div>\n<div><br><\/div>\n<div>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0The night is a clock chiming <br>\n<\/div>\n<div>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0The days go by not I<br>\n<\/div>\n<div><br><\/div>\n<div class=\"credit\">\n                                    Guillaume Apollinaire. \"Mirabeau Bridge\" from <em>Alcools<\/em>, English translation copyright 1995 Donald Revell and reprinted by permission of Wesleyan University Press.<br><br>\n                \n                                    Source: <em>Alcools<\/em><em>(Wesleyan University Press, 1995)<\/em><div class=\"bio-image\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.poetryfoundation.org\/poems-and-poets\/poets\/detail\/guillaume-apollinaire\"><img src=\"https:\/\/media.poetryfoundation.org\/m\/image\/26\/guillaume-apollinaire.jpg\" width=\"160\"><\/a><\/div>\n<h4>Guillaume Apollinaire<\/h4>\n<p class=\"bio\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.poetryfoundation.org\/poems-and-poets\/poets\/detail\/guillaume-apollinaire\">Biography<\/a><br><a href=\"http:\/\/www.poetryfoundation.org\/poems-and-poets\/poets\/detail\/guillaume-apollinaire#about\" data-view=\"ToTopView\">More poems by this author<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<img src=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/~r\/PoetryFoundation\/PoemOfTheDayText\/~4\/tqdOYpGXI1g\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\">\n",
